    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Bebaiotes banksi (Metcalf, 1938), male genitalia: A. Anal tube, pygofer and gonostyli, posterior view; B. Pygofer, lateral view; C. Anal tube, dorsal view; D. Gonostyli, right lateral view; E. Gonostyli, left dorsal view; F. Periandrium and inner sclerotised plates, lateral view; G. Periandrium and inner sclerotised plates, dorsal view. Scale bars: A–G = 0.1 mm." ;
