<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681219>
    dc:description "FIGURE 26. Bebaiotes pennyi sp. nov., male genitalia: A. Anal tube, pygofer and gonostyli, posterior view; B. Pygofer, lateral view; C. Anal tube, dorsal view; D. Gonostyli, left lateral view; E. Gonostyli, dorsal view; F. Periandrium and inner sclerotised plates, lateral view; G. Periandrium and inner sclerotised plates, dorsal view. Scale bars: A–G = 0.1 mm." ;
