<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10681221>
    dc:description "FIGURE 27. Bebaiotes pennyi sp. nov., female: A. Anal tube, dorsal view; B. Pygofer posterior view; C. Gonoplac (third valvula), lateral view; D. Gonapophysis IX (second valvula), dorsal view; E. Gonapophysis VIII (first valvula), lateral view. Scale bars: A–E = 0.1 mm." ;
