    dc:description "FIGURE 41. Wings of Bebaiotes species. A. Bebaiotes pennyi sp. nov., forewing; B. Bebaiotes pennyi sp. nov., hind wing; C. Bebaiotes pulla Muir, 1934, forewing; D. Bebaiotes pulla Muir, 1934, hind wing; E. Bebaiotes tigrina sp. nov., forewing; F. Bebaiotes tigrina sp. nov., hind wing; G. Bebaiotes wilsoni sp. nov., forewing; H. Bebaiotes wilsoni sp. nov., hind wing. Scale bars: A–H = 1 mm." ;
